headline: Concentric Energy Advisors Welcomes Ashley Botelho as an Assistant Vice President
summary: Concentric Energy Advisors, Inc. ("Concentric"), a recognized leader in management consulting services to the North American energy and water industries, continues to expand its regulatory expertise with the strategic hire of Ms. Ashley Botelho as an Assistant Vice President.
